<font size=-1 face="Arial" color="#cc0000"><STRONG>Feature:</STRONG></font> Whether he's "for hire" or prowling Vega$, actor Robert

Urich has saved the day more than once.  But his latest role as a

crimestopper won't be seen.  In fact that is the whole idea behind a

stealthy computer security product called CyberAngel that Robert's involved

with. <p> 



Hear how "Spenser" got motivated by data security, how a stolen machine can

help itself, and the digital future of entertainment from Robert and his

CyberAngel business partner Dr. Dyrk Halstead.<p>

                        







                        







