<br>
The JavaOS debuts at JavaOne...Bill Gates says you'll soon get a full PC for $500...Kodak, MS to move online photos faster, better...

<p>

<a href="/Radio/Vault/Vaulted_96/May_96/5_28_96/">May 28, 1996-- The JavaOne Worldwide Developers Conference is under way this week</a>
<br>
Pac Bell makes consumer Net debut...Pushing CD-ROM quality over a dial-up connect...Trading ads for free access...

<p>

<a href="/Radio/Vault/Vaulted_96/May_96/5_24_96/">May 24, 1996-- This week on <i>CNET Central</i></a>
<br>
