cellspacing=0 cellpadding=5>


<tr>     


<td align=left width=155>


<span class="shorttakes">


<font size=-1 face="Arial", "Helvetica">

<strong><a href="tc/tc11_06_96a.html">Smart cards not so smart</strong></a>
<br>





The reason I use Visa, MasterCard, or American Express instead of a 
debit card is the possibility of an error. With a smart card, the cash 
is gone. With a credit or cash card, you get to review every purchase 20 
days later to ensure bogus purchases aren't listed. 

&nbsp;--Doug Ross, 
dir@worldnet.att.net, 11/6/96

	



